      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、どりきゅんとの再戦の詳細が決まったぞ\n日程はちょうど一ヶ月後。場所は前回と同じだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ I have the details about the rematch with DoriKyun.\nThe date is exactly one month from now‚ and the location is the same as last time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9782956589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "要望通り、再戦までになるべくライブバトルを\n入れておいたからな。一戦一戦大事にしていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you requested‚ I’ve put in as many live battles as possible\nuntil the rematch‚ so let’s take each one seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
